commitMessage:
@@@[CALCITE-2355] Implement multiset operations (Sergey Nuyanzin)

Implement multiset operations: IS A SET.  SUBMULTISET OF.  MEMBER OF. 
MULTISET EXCEPT/INTESECT/UNION [ALL | DISTINCT].  FUSION; add
multiset operations: IS NOT A SET.  IS EMPTY.  IS NOT EMPTY.  SUBMULTISET OF.

Fix behavior if neither ALL nor DISTINCT is specified for the case of
MULTISET EXCEPT/INTERSECT/UNION.

Close apache/calcite#727

@@@[CALCITE-3892] Make junit test classes and methods non-public where possible

Prior to junit 5.  classes and methods had to be public. This is no
longer the case.

Some classes need to remain public because they are referenced from
elsewhere.  or if they use reflection somehow. The remaining 'public'
keyword will be informative to maintainers.
